# ==========================================================================
# CONFIDENTIAL CLIENT DATA — NEVER COMMIT
# The dataset contains a real driving-school client's internal price sheets,
# business questionnaire, and consultation protocols. The entire data/ tree
# and any derived/extracted artifacts stay local only.
# ==========================================================================
data/
*.pdf
*.PDF
# Exception: the public, client-anonymous project documentation PDF (no prices, no
# client PDFs, no PII inside it — verified before every commit). Everything else
# matching *.pdf stays blocked.
!docs/PROJECT_DOCUMENTATION.pdf

# Extracted / derived client content (prices, business info) — confidential
*.client.json
processed/
interim/

# n8n orchestration layer: prepared chunks (real client prices/text) and any
# exported Qdrant snapshots stay local. Only workflow.json, scripts, and docs are public.
n8n/data/
n8n/qdrant_storage/
n8n/workflow_id.txt
n8n/eval_results_raw.json

